member.name: IMAGEHLP_DEFERRED_SYMBOL_LOAD64
member.summary: Contains information about a deferred symbol load.

member.name: IMAGEHLP_DEFERRED_SYMBOL_LOAD64.SizeOfStruct
member.summary: The size of the structure, in bytes. The caller must set this member to sizeof(IMAGEHLP_DEFERRED_SYMBOL_LOAD64).

member.name: IMAGEHLP_DEFERRED_SYMBOL_LOAD64.BaseOfImage
member.summary: The base virtual address where the image is loaded.

member.name: IMAGEHLP_DEFERRED_SYMBOL_LOAD64.CheckSum
member.summary: The computed checksum of the image. This value can be zero.

member.name: IMAGEHLP_DEFERRED_SYMBOL_LOAD64.TimeDateStamp
member.summary: The date and timestamp value. The value is represented in the number of seconds elapsed since midnight (00:00:00), January 1, 1970, Universal Coordinated Time, according to the system clock. The timestamp can be printed using the C run-time (CRT) function ctime.

member.name: IMAGEHLP_DEFERRED_SYMBOL_LOAD64.FileName
member.summary: The image name. The name may or may not contain a full path.

member.name: IMAGEHLP_DEFERRED_SYMBOL_LOAD64.Reparse
member.summary: If this member is TRUE, the operation should be performed again. Otherwise, it should not.

member.name: IMAGEHLP_DEFERRED_SYMBOL_LOAD64.hFile
member.summary: A handle to a file. This member is used with CBA_DEFERRED_SYMBOL_LOAD_PARTIAL and IMAGEHLP_DEFERRED_SYMBOL_LOAD_FAILURE callbacks.
